cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use SpatialScope, please cite the software and the associated Cell article below."
title: "SpatialScope"
version: "1.0"
date-released: 2026-07-18
type: software
authors:
  - family-names: "Liu"
    given-names: "Fengshuo"
repository-code: "https://github.com/fengshuoliu/SpatialScope"
license: "MIT"
abstract: >-
  Native macOS application for spatial image analysis from aligned per-marker
  numeric matrices, including composite visualization, nuclei segmentation,
  cell type assignment, neighborhood analysis, region analysis, cell
  distribution analysis, distance analysis, and publication-ready exports.
